  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study aims at evaluating in normal weight and obese subjects those factors such as taste
      sensitivity and circulating endocannabinoids in influencing dietary choice and thereby lipid
      and energy metabolism in order to design personalized nutritional strategies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
